+Cac thao tac copy,cut,paste,delete
Dat con nhay tu dau doan van muon copy hoac cut roi keo con nhay xuong
M-w: copy
C-w: delete
Di chuyen con cho den vi tri ta muon dan roi bam C-y de paste
Cut: delete -> paste
